# Others: Deliverables & Documentation

This folder contains project documentation, deliverables, and non-code assets.

## Contents
- Project reports and documentation
- Design documents and specifications
- Meeting minutes and notes
- Presentations and demos
- Research papers and references

## Organization Suggestions
- /docs - Technical documentation
- /reports - Project reports and analysis
- /presentations - Slides and presentations
- /deliverables - Final project deliverables

## Team Notes
- Keep documentation up-to-date
- Follow naming conventions for files
- Include dates on reports and presentations